OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FThe head of the Metropolitan Police
OL,7,Fhas said the force are investigating
OL,8,Fwhether an Islamist group with
OL,9,Fpossible Iranian state links is behind
OL,10,Fan arson attack on Jewish community
OL,11,Fambulances.
OL,13,FThe incident in Golders Green, north-
OL,14,Fwest London, in which four vehicles
OL,15,Fwere destroyed in the early hours of
OL,16,FMonday, is being treated as an
OL,17,Fantisemitic hate crime but not as
OL,18,Fterrorism, Scotland Yard has said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FA video has allegedly been posted on
OL,7,FTelegram by an Islamist group called
OL,8,FHarakat Ashab al-Yamin al-Islamia,
OL,9,Fshowing a map of the location where
OL,10,Fthe ambulances were kept and footage
OL,11,Fof them on fire.
OL,13,FSpeaking on Monday at the annual
OL,14,Fdinner of the Community Security Trust
OL,15,F(CST), a charity that monitors
OL,16,Fantisemitism in the UK, Sir Mark
OL,17,FRowley said the "rapid growth in
OL,18,Frecent years of Iranian state threats
OL,19,Fis grave", but it was "too early" to
OL,20,Fattribute the attack to the Iranian
OL,21,Fstate.
OL,26,@yD@QOU{D@IO]{D@WOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FSir Mark said: "Britain's Jewish
OL,7,Fcommunity has in recent years been
OL,8,Fincreasingly targeted by individuals,
OL,9,Fgroups and hostile states, intent on
OL,10,Fspreading fear, hate and harm.
OL,12,F"This volatile mix is at the front of
OL,13,Fmy mind given events of today."
OL,15,FHe added: "The rapid growth in recent
OL,16,Fyears of Iranian state threats is
OL,17,Fgrave: hostile state surveillance
OL,18,Factivity, 20 disrupted plots, and
OL,19,Frecent attempted attacks on the
OL,20,FIranian diaspora.
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOUuD@_O]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,F"None of this is isolated.
OL,8,F"It is part of a rapidly shifting
OL,9,Fthreat landscape.
OL,11,F"It is too early for me to attribute
OL,12,Flast night's attack in Golders Green
OL,13,Fto the Iranian state ` that is rightly
OL,14,Ffor the counter-terrorism
OL,15,Finvestigation to determine ` but
OL,16,Fwhoever was responsible, the impact is
OL,17,Fserious.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,F"We believe three suspects were
OL,7,Finvolved and we are pursuing all lines
OL,8,Fof inquiry, including an online claim
OL,9,Fof responsibility by an Islamist group
OL,10,Fwho have claimed other attacks across
OL,11,FEurope and have potential Iranian
OL,12,Fstate links."
OL,14,FCCTV shows three people in hoods
OL,15,Fpouring accelerant on the vehicles,
OL,16,Fwhich belong to Jewish community
OL,17,Fambulance service Hatzola, before
OL,18,Fsetting them on fire and running away.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
