CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FSpeaking near the scene on Monday,
OL,7,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,8,FWilliams, who leads policing for the
OL,9,Farea, said investigators are aware of
OL,10,Fa group apparently claiming
OL,11,Fresponsibility for the attack online,
OL,12,Fbut have not yet verified whether this
OL,13,Fis true.
OL,15,FSir Mark praised the "extraordinary
OL,16,Fspeed and professionalism" of local
OL,17,Fvolunteers, CST teams, synagogue
OL,18,Fsecurity and Hatzola staff, which he
OL,19,Fsaid "quite literally protected
OL,20,Flives", alongside the actions of Met
OL,21,Fofficers.
OL,26,@wD@VOUxD@ZO]{D@FOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
