OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FHe added: "And let us be clear about
OL,7,Fwhat was targeted: a volunteer
OL,8,Fambulance service that serves
OL,9,Feveryone, of every background.
OL,11,F"An attack on Hatzola is not only an
OL,12,Fattack on the Jewish community but an
OL,13,Fattack on all of us.
OL,15,F"There is no us and them. There is
OL,16,Fonly an attack on a British community."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUwD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
