OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FSir Mark said his force's aim was "to
OL,7,Fprotect, to be visible, to offer
OL,8,Freassurance and to keep people safe"
OL,9,Fand said additional measures are being
OL,10,Fput in place to protect Jewish
OL,11,Fcommunities.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,14,Fcalled for communities to "all stand
OL,15,Ftogether" in the face of the "horrific
OL,16,Fantisemitic attack", while Chief Rabbi
OL,17,FEphraim Mirvis said the targeting of
OL,18,Fthe volunteer service was
OL,19,F"particularly sickening".
OL,26,@nD@cOUpD@dO]vD@[OUwD@IO]wD@^OUxD@SO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
