OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FNearby homes were evacuated as a
OL,7,Fprecaution and road closures in the
OL,8,Farea remain in place.
OL,10,FResidents described being woken in the
OL,11,Fearly hours by the noise, with the
OL,12,Fforce of the explosions blowing out
OL,13,Fwindows, including those of the nearby
OL,14,Fsynagogue.
OL,16,FOne man, who lives in Highfield Road,
OL,17,Fsaid: "My wife was afraid for her
OL,18,Flife. People were shouting to just
OL,19,Fgrab a bag and leave but did not tell
OL,20,Fus where to go. It was very scary and
OL,21,FI'm still shaking now."
OL,26,@yD@GOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
