OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FCounter Terrorism Police, who are
OL,7,Fleading the investigation, are
OL,8,Fappealing for anyone with footage of
OL,9,Fthe arson attack to get in touch.
OL,11,FJewish leaders met the Prime Minister
OL,12,Fin Downing Street on Monday, and
OL,13,FMichael Wegier, chief executive of the
OL,14,FBoard of Deputies of British Jews,
OL,15,Fsaid Jews in the UK feel less safe now
OL,16,Fthan a few years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
