OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FOn Monday evening, more than 250
OL,7,Fpeople attended a rally against
OL,8,Fantisemitism in Golders Green,
OL,9,Faccording to Press Association
OL,10,Festimates.
OL,12,FProtesters waved the Israeli flag and
OL,13,Fchanted "Keir Starmer, Jew harmer",
OL,14,F"Long live Israel" and "No to Jew
OL,15,Fhate".
OL,26,@uD@IOUuD@bO]vD@AOUvD@RO]vD@XOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
