CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FThe chief executive of the Campaign
OL,7,FAgainst Antisemitism (CAA) told the
OL,8,Frally the arson attack was
OL,9,F"calculated" and "despicable", and
OL,10,Fformer home secretary Suella Braverman
OL,11,Fsaid the incident was "not a surprise"
OL,12,Fas the Jewish community are "living
OL,13,Fwith normalised antisemitism".
OL,15,FA police cordon around the scene was
OL,16,Flifted later and Highfield Road was
OL,17,Freopened at 8.45pm.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@LO]qD@ROUqD@]O]sD@WOUsD@fO]tD@
OL,26,A]OUuD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
