OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FThree community ambulances could be
OL,7,Fseen completely burnt out and a fourth
OL,8,Fappeared to be more intact, with
OL,9,Fsignificant damage to the bonnet of
OL,10,Fthe vehicle.
OL,12,FThe latest official figures on hate
OL,13,Fcrime recorded by police in England
OL,14,Fand Wales showed Jewish people had the
OL,15,Fhighest rate of religious hate crimes
OL,16,Ftargeted at them of any faith group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774335860
OL,3,CMet chief says rise in Iranian state
OL,4,Cthreats 'grave' after arson attack
OL,6,FTwo worshippers were killed in a
OL,7,Fdeadly attack on a synagogue in
OL,8,FManchester in October 2025 and, in a
OL,9,Fseparate investigation earlier this
OL,10,Fmonth, two men were charged with
OL,11,Fallegedly spying on Jewish people and
OL,12,Flocations for Iran.
OL,14,FThe Government has pledged to fund
OL,15,Freplacements for the ambulances as
OL,16,Fwell as immediate health support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
